    "In the USA, insurance type is related to a range of socioeconomic, demographic and employment factors which are also determinants of health outcomes (Ross and Mirowsky, 2000; Bittoni et al., 2015; Su et al., 2019; Keisler-Starkey and Bunch, 2020).",
    "Insurance information was therefore included with the intention that it should serve as a proxy for these wider determinants.",
    "These patient records were ordered sequentially and an array was created for each patient.",
    "Figure 1 shows how the patient timelines were constructed.",
    "In EHR data, the sequence of codes within visits is typically not preserved in the data."
